@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+config FRAG_ENTROPY
+	tristate "SLUB fragmentation and memory entropy generator"
+	depends on m
+	help
+	  This module induces SLUB cache fragmentation and increases memory 
+	  entropy by performing randomized allocations and deallocations.
+	  It culminates in a persistent memory bloat of 10% of total system RAM.
+	  
+	  This is intended for testing memory pressure and fragmentation 
+	  scenarios and should only be built as a module.
